OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FA sunny
OL,6,Fevening for most but some low cloud
OL,7,Fwill affect the east. Dry with clear
OL,8,Fspells and becoming rather chilly
OL,9,Fovernight with some low cloud
OL,10,Fspreading inland.
OL,11,
OL,12,CTuesday:FEarly low cloud will mostly
OL,13,Fburn off but some will continue to
OL,14,Fafflict the coasts. Otherwise, another
OL,15,Fdry day with plenty of sunshine and
OL,16,Fbecoming warm inland.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
